titleEN: Scrap Metal Life Size Alien Statue
content: Pay homage to one the greatest sci-fi horror films of all time by adding this scrap metal life size alien statue to your collection. This daunting statue stands at 8 feet tall and is masterfully crafted entirely from scrap and recycled metal parts.

Warn your unsuspecting co-workers of your unpleasantness in a humorous way with this hangry definition coffee mug. The black wording is displayed against a white background to appear like a realistic definition entry.

The Tetris game coffee table is the ideal way to pass the time when you’re relaxing at home. This one-of-a-kind table comes with a built-in scratch and water resistant LCD top that allows you to play classic games like Tetris and Snake using a gamepad controller.

At long last, educators everywhere will be able to accurately grade essays with help from the bullshit stamp. Whenever a slacker tries to pass off their B.S. as well-researched material, just bust out this stamp and mark that bullshit off accordingly.

If I fits, I sits. With the fuzzy bubble cat bed your quirky ninja cat can hide from the outside world in a cozy little wool ball of fuzziness. Available in a variety of colors, the bubble cat bed is perfect for when a cat needs some alone time with his catnip.

Let the good times roll in LEGOville by adding this Bob Ross LEGO set to your collection. The set comes with a tiny Bob Ross LEGO figure – complete with a 70s inspired outfit and a killer afro-perm – and a painter’s palette, easel, jars of paint, and canvas.

Proudly display your family of  traveling entertainers with the Aristocrats family car sticker! Showcasing their signature performance, the Aristocrats family car sticker tells the world that you are a close knit family who has what it takes to make it in show business.

Brix is the modular shelving system ideal for storing everything from books to BluRays to shoes to anything else you can fit inside. They’re crafted from high strength cardboard and can be placed in virtually any configuration you wish.

Bring a touch of whimsy to your reading space by keeping your vast literary collection in the spiral bookshelf. The bold minimalist design of the structure helps save space while adding an eye-catching accent piece to the room.

Is that a kitten purring in your panties or are you just happy to see me? Comfortable and fashionable, these frisky panties come with a cute kitty cat plastered on the front and make the purrfect pair of undergarments for a crazy exhibitionist cat lady.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Bed Star Canopy
content: Make bedtime an enchanting and star-filled experience with the glow in the dark bed star canopy. The canopy protects from pesky nighttime creepy crawlers while creating a magical starry sky that you’re unlikely to find in any urban environment.

Make your humble abode glow with an earthly charm by illuminating the room with the tree roots chandelier. This unique light fixture is handcrafted from pewter wires that are bent and twisted together to form a massive system of tree roots.

Make your formal wear pop during the night by accenting your dapper suit with one of these light up bow ties. This custom accessory is outfitted with a vibrant glow wire around the edges that shines bright for over 12 hours.

Teach your favorite feline how to party the right way with some catnip joints. Legal in all 50 states, these hand stuffed and hand rolled joints are filled with a generous serving of some premium catnip so your kitty will be entertained for hours.

Stay springtime fresh all year round by rubbing shit all over yourself using this dog poop soap. Despite its off putting and realistic appearance, this novelty soap features a delightful chocolate scent and doubles as a great prop for pranks.

Become the living embodiment of your favorite video game character by dressing up in this Final Fantasy Cloud Strife costume. This handmade ensemble is tailored to your exact measurements and is based on Cloud’s outfit from Final Fantasy 7.

Channel your inner fairy and make your outfit pop with color by slipping into a pair of these flowered fishnet stockings. Each of these one-of-a-kind fishnets come accented with lovely handmade floral designs that create a whimsical fairy-like feel.

Make your feline friend purr with joy by moving him into one of these fairy tale cat cave houses. Each house offers a whimsical Dr. Seuss inspired designs that is complemented with wild and vivid color schemes and designs.

Straight out of bat country comes a surreal piece of art for your cinematic collection – the Fear and Loathing In Las Vegas movie sculpture. The iconic movie poster of the cult film comes alive as it’s masterfully recreated from silicone.

Give your offspring’s wardrobe a much needed power up with these superhero onesies. Instead of cutesy little animals, these handmade onesies come designed like the uniforms of various iconic heroes such as Han Solo, Captain Planet, or the Power Rangers.

Let your submissive know who’s in charge in the bedroom by spicing up your love life with this pentagram leather harness. This unholy little number is crafted from black leather and accented with a hellish satanic looking cat at the center.

Give Mr. Whiskers the secluded lounge area he deserves by installing the cat bridge in your home. This handmade item offers your kitty cat a secure spot to relax in – or even re-enact your favorite scenes from Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom.

Do you love tetanus shots? If so, you’ll love showering with these rusty razor blades wedged inside of a soap bar! These custom glycerin soaps features a sharp razor blade lodged in the middle that’ll keep you on your toes as you clean your more intimate areas.

Rev up your humble abode’s decor by parking one of these refurbished car couches in your living room. Each quirky couch is expertly made using the body of an old salvaged car that is complemented with a comfy and stylish leather seating.

Put the finishing touch on your cool post-apocalyptic getup by accenting it with these custom biohazard sneakers. Each unique pair is styled with natural fabric, genuine leather, and an impossible to miss biohazard symbol with a skull at the center.

Give your home a distinguished appearance by creating an inviting ambiance with this industrial lighting fixture. This eye-catching home decor gives off a warm yellowish glow and comes outfitted with vintage styled bulbs to give the room some added character.

Highlight your perfectly symmetrical rack with these attention grabbing light up nipple pasties. Available in several styles including flashing blue stars, and multi-colored “what am I doing with my life?” daisies, they’re the most fashionable way to disappoint your parents.

Give yourself an animated comic strip appearance with these cel shaded jeans. These Borderlands inspired jeans have been expertly decorated with specialized fabric paint that creates the illusion you’re wearing cartoon jeans.

Protect your home against all kinds of intruders by beefing up your security with this recycled metal robot sculpture. This imposing work of art stands at eight and a half feet tall and comes outfitted with LED accents that make his torso and parts of his legs glow.

Keep your little monsters entertained for hours without spending a fortune by filling their tiny hands with soft serve slime. This gooey, thick, and stretchy slime is available in containers ranging from two to eight ounces and comes in a range of wild colors.

Give your modern smartwatch an antiquated feel by encasing it in this steampunk copper Apple watch cover. Each handmade cover is made to order and crafted from cast copper and is available in either a distressed or polished surface.

Take your meals from bland to exotic by infusing them with a dash of flavor courtesy of the Indian spice kit. These rare and sought after spices will revamp your tired recipes and send your tastebuds on an alluring journey to the land of India with every bite.

Show off your gluttonous pizza devouring ways by wearing this satirical “Pizza Slut” shirt in public. This shirt plays on the Pizza Hut logo in a creative way, making it a top fashion choice for lovers of the timeless recipe of tossed dough, red sauce, and cheese.

Cement the bond between you and your closest buds with this pizza slice friendship necklace. No matter how many home slices you have in your inner circle, this golden pie can be customized with as many pizza slices as you need.

The Alice in Wonderland doorknob is no hallucination. Although he doesn’t talk much – unless you’re under the influence – the doorknob provides a nostalgic and whimsical decor to any room that no Alice In Wonderland’s fan should be without.

Bring the majesty of the deep sea into your own home when you light up your room with the hanging jellyfish lamps. These astonishingly realistic lamps are handmade in various pastel colors and give off a soft glow as they gracefully float overhead.

Give your kids the joy and happiness you could only dream of as a child by installing the storybook tree house in your yard. The combination of the hollowed out tree, slide and clubhouse provide the ideal hangout spot for hours of entertainment.

Your little princess is finally coming of age and that means one thing – <del>pedophile</del> teenage vampires. And the only way to ward off the advances of these sparkley immortals is to purchase one of these fully functional vampire killing kits.

Give your autumn themed style a lovely natural touch by accenting your look using this glass acorn necklace. This handmade gem features a quaint little 20mm x 16mm glass acorn pendant available in a range of fall hues like rich apricot, sage, merlot, and wheat.

Treat your sophisticated palate to a hodgepodge of refined ingredients by digging into one of these 24K gold champagne marshmallows. Each of these champagne infused treats are made with a rich Belgian chocolate and topped off with 24K gold foil.

Go from plain Jane to Nordic warrior by putting on this fantasy viking leather helm. It’s handmade from genuine leather and accented with two imposing flexible ram-like horns crafted from resin and expertly painted in the color of your choosing.

Take on your city’s rampant crime problem single-handedly by hitting the mean streets dressed in this Dark Knight Rises batsuit. Styled like Bruce’s iconic crime-fighting getup, it’s accented with a golden utility belt and his signature bat symbol across the chest.

titleEN: People I Want To Punch In The Face Book
content: Screw the high road! Give into your vengeful ways by keeping track of everyone that wronged you with the “People I Want To Punch In The Face” book. The book provides ample room to write down the countless individuals who’ve made the mistake of crossing you.

Yarrr – raise the anchors and set sail for fun and adventure when playing aboard the custom pirate ship playhouse. This marooned pirate ship boasts a sturdy concrete and wood design that make this the ultimate hangout spot for booty plunderers.

Keep track of your health and armor at all times while staying informed of the time with the 007 GoldenEye watch. This unisex watch sports a classy stainless steel band and comes painstakingly decorated with the iconic health and armor bands from the N64 game.

Now you can get your idea, story, or even marriage proposal converted into a cute animated short by ordering one of these personalized cartoon flipbooks. Simply provide your personal details and photos – and Ben Zuraswski will turn them into a flipbook.

Bombard your palate with delicious and fattening sugar by indulging in some Millennium Falcon chocolate. Handmade from the finest ingredients in the galaxy, these savory treats are shaped and colored to resemble Han Solo’s flagship vessel.

Turn your favorite emoji into your number one snack by baking up a batch of poop emoji cookies. The cookie cutter is crafted from a dishwasher safe PLA plastic and is available in sizes that range from a small 2″ x 2″ mold to a larger 5″ x 5″ turd mold.

Bring chivalry back to the twenty-first century by protecting your family’s honor while dressed in the medieval armor set.  This wearable costume covers your entire head and torso in distinguished stainless steel plates to protect you in the heat of battle.

Transform your home into a fun dollhouse by commissioning a custom miniature of your humble abode. Simply send in pictures and measurements of your home and you’ll receive a detailed tiny architectural model of your home.

Complement your ever growing movie prop collection with the imposing Ghostbusters Vigo Replica painting. This larger-than-life painting depicts Vigo the Carpathian as he stands against a 16th century backdrop and ominously peers into your soul.

The Oreo cheesecake cookies are the delicious homemade treat that tastes so good they’ll absolutely be worth all the weight you’re bound to gain. With each order you’ll receive a dozen fresh treats that are crisp and crunchy on the outside and gooey on the inside.

Give your cutthroat match some visual appeal by squaring off against your opponent on this nixie tube chessboard. This one of a kind handmade board lights up the pieces using built-in induction coils, requiring absolutely no plugs.

Give your high tech laptop a rustic appearance that’ll turn heads by using this wood MacBook keyboard. Made with a real mahogany veneer, each key features a pressure sensitive adhesive backing that makes installation remarkably easy.

Transform your little princess into a fabled sea-creature by slipping her into this adorable baby mermaid costume. This handmade ensemble comes with a flower headband, a shell bikini top, and a mermaid fin woven from acrylic yarn.

Make your house a home by giving it a unique scent all of its own with this Dachshund dog farts candle. This handmade candle sports a red hue, features a delightful scent made up of almond biscotti and cherry cordial, and comes in a delightful 8 oz mason jar.

Time travel is within your reach with the flux capacitor nixie tube clock. This handmade flux capacitor replica lights up just like the one in the movie as it displays the time in an easy to read analog format. And the best part of all, it requires no plutonium!

Experience a level of comfort so powerful it’s enough to make you enter hibernation when you lay down on the grizzly bear bean bag. Designed like an over-sized snuggly grizzly, the bean bag features knitted graphics on a washable cover designed for everyday use.

Create professional quality prints without needing formal training by using this pattern paint roller. This easy to use painting accessory comes imprinted with a delightful pattern that you simply roll in paint and then onto the wall to create amazing designs.

Add a magical twist to your reading sessions by using this unique Harry Potter glasses bookmark.  Laser cut from powder coated metal, it features a long slender frame that is complemented by a pair of tiny circular Potter-style spectacles.

Drown your cares away in a nice warm tub by dropping this cherry blossom bath bomb. This bath bomb comes adorned with a pink cherry blossom design and is given a delicate scent that will soothe your mind and body.

No self respecting eccentric rave outfit would be complete without a touch of this fluorescent UV body paint. This latex-free hypo-allergenic cream based paint is available in five vivid colors including red, yellow, orange, green, and blue.

Protect your bedroom from the treacherous Calamity Ganon using this Zelda Master sword replica. The sword is handmade from wood, Styrofoam, silk floral, dried moss, with a design inspired by the Breath of the Wild game.

Help your house feel more like home by decorating it using the “Bless This Motherfucking Home” stitch. Made with love in every stitch, this quaint little portrait comes in a lovely wooden frame and features a blunt message that’ll add warmth to any home.

Give your formal attire an eye-catching touch that screams class and style by accenting your suit with the snakeskin tie. This vintage piece comes straight from the far-out 1970s and is made of premium silk and the finest snakeskin this side of the Mississippi.

Easily add a touch of color and natural beauty to your bedroom with this beautiful artificial plant forest terrarium. The glass dome displays a gorgeous natural setting composed entirely of high quality artificial plants that won’t ever dry up and wither away.

Flirt with danger when you pull out this .357 Magnum gun hair dryer. It is the perfect beauty accessory for true cowgirls who love to pull the trigger on over the top hair styles, and it also makes a cool prop for photos.

Impress everyone at the costume party when you show up as the embodiment of Alphonse Elric in this Full Metal Alchemist steel armor. It’s made of steel and leather for maximum authenticity while allowing you to comfortably walk around and sit.

Smell like an adorable little kitty kat by spraying yourself with this kitten fur perfume. This unique fragrance captures the olfactory essence of the warmth and comfort of that purrfect spot located just behind a kitten’s neck.

Add authenticity to your alternate Star Wars universe ensemble by completing your look using these steampunk lightsabers. Each custom lightsaber is meticulously crafted to look like a battle hardened Jedi weapon from a galaxy far far away.

Give your generic laptop a unique appearance by splashing a bit of color on it using this dripping paint MacBook keyboard cover. The cover protects your keyboard from dust, scratches, and general wear and tear while the abstract design creates an artsy feel.

Walk onto the battlefield with confidence wielding a sword in one hand and one of these handmade combat shields in the other. Ideal for medieval combat games, each shield features a viking inspired design that’s handmade with authenticity in mind.

Gear up for battle with Superman – or Comic Con – by getting into this Batman armored suit costume. Modeled after the Caped Crusader’s imposing suit, it’s expertly crafted from EVA foam to facilitate movement and accented with LEDs for added authenticity.

Admire the beauty of our planetary neighbors up close and personal by switching on one of these solar system lamps. The colorful and vibrant paint job on each spherical lamp makes it come to life as it radiates a soft glow that’s perfect for accent lighting.

titleEN: Don’t Fuck Up The Table Coasters
content: Keep your goddamn house guests from ruining your motherfucking furniture using these “don’t fuck up the table” coasters. Each coaster is made from thick blotter paper and comes printed with a short and not so sweet message that’ll immediately catch anyone’s attention.

Stay fashionable while you’re busy getting nothing done by slipping into this “Just Do It Later” shirt. This novelty shirt spoofs Nike’s iconic “just do it” slogan to better reflect your lazy and unmotivated lifestyle.

Help the Rebels defeat the Empire by power-napping your way through the afternoon on the Admiral Ackbar pillowcase. This Star Wars themed pillowcase displays a portrait of the valiant Admiral along with his most famous line – “It’s a <del>trap</del> nap”.

Highlight your curvaceous features with this heart cutout ass cleavage panties. These risque pair of unmentionables are handmade from ultra soft microfiber and accented with a small white bow located above the heart cutout.

titleEN: Magic The Gathering Death Star Card
content: Increase your chances of victory by incorporating this non-regulation Magic the Gathering Death Star card in your deck. This one of a kind card was made utilizing an actual foil card from the game, making this a great gift for any MTG or Star Wars fans.

Set your spicy food loving friend’s insides on fire  with this super hot chili gift set. This gift set lets you sample three variations of some of the world’s hottest peppers like the Carolina Reaper, the Moruga Scorpion, and the Naga Bhut Jolokia pepper.

titleEN: Beauty & The Beast Rose Vial Necklace
content: Give your look a regal touch fit for royalty by putting on this Beauty and the Beast rose vial necklace. This darling little accent piece features a small handmade rose shedding its brightly colored pedals inside the small glass vial.

Experience one of your favorite board games like never before when you try to out-settle everyone else playing on the 3D Settlers of Catan tiles. The tiles come intricately designed to reveal every corner of the breathtaking island vistas.

Cultivate a serene environment in any part of your hectic home by growing your own bonsai red maple tree. With these seeds you’ll be able to relax yourself while taking part in the ancient tradition of planting and maintaining your very own miniature tree.

Increase your chances of survival when all hell breaks loose by making sure you keep the apocalypse survival bug out bag by your side. This life-saving backpack comes jam packed with everything necessary to keep two people alive when society collapses.

Bathe like a true Pokemon master by unleashing a flurry of colored bubbles with the Pokeball bath bomb. Once placed in the water, the Pokeball dissolves and dyes the water blue as it simultaneously sets free a little Pokemon contained inside of it.

Turn the mundane task of turning on the lights into a unnecessarily complex procedure with the overcomplicated light switch cover. These custom covers come with a variety of intricate designs that are true marvels of over-engineering.

Turn any dull garden into a technicolored wonderland with these rainbow colored roses. The roses germinate with incredible ease, making them ideal for gardeners of all skill sets who are looking for an eye catching centerpiece for their yards.

When life’s got you feeling blue, it helps to have a little pick me up. Shit’s Fucked: A Positivity Guide is a short help book with little tips about feeling better about your day and improving your overall mindset. If nothing else, the book cover will definitely give you a laugh.

titleEN: His & Hers Toiler Paper Cup Holders
content: Now you can stay hydrated while you’re spending quality time on the porcelain goddess thanks to these his and hers toilet paper cup holders. These 3D printed attachments are specially customized to easily accommodate both beer cans and fancy stemware.

Get to know your favorite city more in depth by examining one of these 3D wood city maps. Unlike conventional 2D maps, these handmade maps allow you to see elements like water depth and land elevation in addition to natural landmarks.

Make your next celebration one to remember using this Instagram photo booth prop. Before being sent to you, the photo is customized with your personal information and then emailed to you so that you can conveniently print  the file and begin snapping away.

Smell as good as a freshly brewed cup of Joe by lathering up with this coffee soap bar. It’s made using natural ingredients and ground roasted coffee beans that provide a gentle exfoliation that will leave your skin feeling softer than ever.

Make your little muggles feel more magical than ever before with these twinkling wizard/witch wands. These handmade wooden wands measure approximately ten inches long and come with custom designs and color combinations.

Marvel at the unparalleled beauty of mother nature up close by gazing at this extremely rare rainbow crystal geode. This gorgeous geode has been cut to reveal a sea of tiny crystals that shine and glimmer when placed under light.

Look like the most stylish virgin in town by accenting your look with this Nintendo controller bandolier/belt. This gamer themed wearable accessory pays homage to the iconic Japanese gaming company by showcasing the controllers from all of their consoles.

Achieve a radiant glow that will turn heads by using this unicorn skin rainbow highlighter. This 100% vegan luminizer delivers a radiant and iridescent glow that is ideal for creating a lighthearted yet simultaneously whimsical look.

Marvel at the beauty of our planetary neighbors by accenting your outfit with this solar system ring set. These handmade rings are made from sterling silver and  are decorated with glass and stone beads to resemble each of the nearby planets.

Transform yourself into an elite member of the Imperial Guard by donning this incredibly detailed Warhammer 40K costume. It’s handmade from EVA foam to facilitate movement and is expertly styled and painted like a Kasrkin soldier.

Give your sleek smartphone an elegant appearance by protecting it against scratches using this marble styled iPhone case. Each of these plastic and acrylic cases are designed to provide a snug, secure fit while still allowing access to all of your phone’s features.

Give your elven warrior costume a touch of authenticity by arming yourself with this bronze leaf claw. The set includes five bronze filigree claws that each display beautiful ornate designs that give the claws a realistic and authentic feel.
